text: Ayukhanovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Rayevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 286 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Davlekanovo, 2 km from Rayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Ayukhanovo
